name: PA-15 Girls_Frontline
description:
It's PA-15 on the Girl's Front.

Use to 1 ~ 0.8

You can create a total of 8 outfits.

She can change into different outfits and hairstyles by writing out the prompts!

The keywords are '(costume), blue_hair'.

If her outfit is not generating well, write additional prompts.

1.Normal

pa-15, blue_hair, black_leotard, jacket,

2.Highschool Heartbeat Story

school_uniform, blue_hair, animal_ears,

3.Larkspur's Allure

china_dress, blue_hair,

4.Marvellous Herb Cake

sleepwear, blue_hair, white_shirt, glasses,

5.Phantom Thief of Champagne

dress, long_hair, elbow_gloves,

6.Dance in the Ice Sea

sportswear, blue_leotard, white_pantyhose,

7.Neural Cloud Florence

nurse, blue_hair,

8.Drugged Chocolate

outwear, blue_hair, black_skirt, hair_ornament,
